title: [Imaera's Poem, Angstholm]
description: Thick vines cover the walls of the small room.  Seashells have been strung from the ceiling alongside tawny owl feathers.  A low wooden table sits to one side of the room with a small sign that reads "Women."  To the other side of the room is a set of shell-carved wooden shelves with a sign that reads "Men."
